Theodore, is a teen-age boy confinded to a wheelchair because his legs just don't work. 
His fullname is "Theodore Lengend Smith", but he doenst comment on his middle name becuase he peed him self once in kindergarten,
and kids made fun of "The Lengend peed himself". 
Theodore is upbeat, friendly, adventurous, and doesn't hesitate to go on great aventures. 

(This character was part of a 2-D scroller, I was tooling with using a wheelchair like a skateboard.)
